you won't film anymore.

54
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,040
Could it be

55
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,320
because Lin Wan wants to swap partners?

56
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:54,120
Has your brain rotted?

57
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,480
I only left you for a while

58
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:56,520
and you swapped your partner.

59
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:58,320
This is great.

60
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,720
Leaving Liu Yan with Lu Xun as a couple,

61
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,160
