with Lu Xun.

64
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,440
Minus the amount to be paid to him,

65
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,280
115,000.

66
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,760
I still have a balance of 885,000.

67
00:03:12,660 --> 00:03:14,020
(Just you wait.
Don't worry!)

68
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:16,320
She really transferred the money to you?

69
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:19,200
Now we don't have to worry about
Lin Wan's medical expenses.

70
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:20,880
This is just the first payment.

71
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:21,520
Three days later,

72
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,800
she will transfer the rest.

73
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:26,280
We signed this contract for just 300,000.

74
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,680
If we calculate this,

75
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:29,280
then we've made
an extra 700,000 for nothing.

76
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:32,480
Now that we put it this way,

77
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,000
it's not impossible to let her

78
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,280
have Lu Xun for three days.

79
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:37,480
We'll just take him back
after three days.

80
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,960
It's a sure win deal.

81
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:40,000
Right?

82
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:46,120
I've always had a feeling

83
